It is perhaps unnecessary for me to adduce any evidence of the carelessness of APV, as that will be apparent to any one who will glance over the readings of a chapter or two in Orelli's edition, but I shall endeavour to show (1) that A and V are independent of each other, but approach more nearly to one another than to any of the other uss, (2) that B is connected with the arche- type by adifferent line of descent from the others, and has frequently preserved the true reading which has been lost by them, but that it also alters the mistaken readings of the archetype so as to make sense.
